data.description: Welcome to a fantastic opportunity to own a meticulously maintained townhome in the esteemed Indian Prairie School District. Nestled in the desirable Windridge Community, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.    Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the warmth of new laminate flooring that extends throughout the first floor, creating a contemporary and inviting atmosphere. The master bathroom has been tastefully updated with new flooring, complemented by fresh paint that enhances the overall aesthetic.    The heart of this townhome lies in its modern open concept on the first floor, promoting a seamless flow between the living spaces. Whether you're entertaining guests or spending quality time with family, the layout is designed to enhance your overall living experience.    The main bedroom is a retreat in itself, boasting generous proportions and featuring a decent-sized walk-in closet. The thoughtful separation of bedrooms by a shared second-floor bathroom ensures privacy and convenience. The second bedroom also offers ample closet space, catering to your storage needs.    Noteworthy upgrades include a new roof and siding implemented in 2018, providing peace of mind and contributing to the property's overall curb appeal. Additionally, the inclusion of a second-floor laundry adds a practical touch to everyday living.    A further update to note is the replacement of the washing machine in April 2023, ensuring that the home is equipped with modern and reliable appliances.    Convenience extends beyond the confines of the home, with easy access to expressways, shopping centers, and a myriad of area amenities. The spacious backyard completes the picture, offering a private outdoor space for relaxation or recreation.    Don't miss the chance to make this townhome your own-schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and functionality of this Indian Prairie gem before it's gone.
